name: .MLPROJ File Extension
summary: Learn about .MLPROJ files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open an MLPROJ (MATLAB Project) file in MathWorks MATLAB (cross-platform). If you have MATLAB installed, you can import the project an MLPROJ file contains by double-clicking the file. MATLAB will then open the Extract Project to dialog box. Specify the location at which you want to save the project, and then click Select Folder. The project your MLPROJ file contains will then open in MATLAB.
